+//! Vectors ensure they never allocate more than `isize::MAX` bytes.
+//!
+//! # Examples
+//!
+//! You can explicitly create a [`Vec`] with [`Vec::new`]:
+//!
+//! ```
+//! let v: Vec<i32> = Vec::new();
+//! ```
+//!
